      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's interesting. Why would the lack of a formal education or steady job be classified as an \"aggravating factor\" in a legal sense? Usually, aggravating factors are things like prior violent felonies or premeditation. Does his background change the way we view his likelihood of reoffending compared to Profile A?",
